sentences: Tatsuya Fukumuro, better known as Nhato or kyu, is a Japanese electronic dance music producer from Tokyo.
While he started making trance, his style is more reminiscent of Dubstep and House now.
He's also a regular on different labels such as Massive CircleZ, and more recently in HARDCORE TANO*C. He also released "Star Trail" for beatmania IIDX.
